In order to avoid saturation, the maximum time that an analysis module can dedicate to carry out an analysis
and tuning process is 1/ fa , the analysis period. This constraint is deÔ¨Åned by the following expression:
N ¬∑ Ea ¬∑ T m + T a (N) +

